WEBVTT

00:00:01.005 --> 00:00:05.973
I was the first woman president

00:00:07.805 --> 00:00:09.465
of an African nation.

00:00:11.719 --> 00:00:18.203
And I do believe more countries
ought to try that.

00:00:18.227 --> 00:00:19.440
(Laughter)

00:00:19.464 --> 00:00:26.464
(Applause and cheers)

00:00:27.292 --> 00:00:30.498
Once the glass ceiling has been broken,